## Remarks  
  
> [!NOTE]
>  <span data-ttu-id="4035b-693">Il <xref:System.Xml.XmlValidatingReader> classe è obsoleta in [!INCLUDE[dnprdnext](~/includes/dnprdnext-md.md)].</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4035b-693">The <xref:System.Xml.XmlValidatingReader> class is obsolete in [!INCLUDE[dnprdnext](~/includes/dnprdnext-md.md)].</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="4035b-694">È possibile creare un oggetto di convalida <xref:System.Xml.XmlReader> quando si utilizza la <xref:System.Xml.XmlReaderSettings> classe e il <xref:System.Xml.XmlReader.Create%2A> (metodo).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4035b-694">You can create a validating <xref:System.Xml.XmlReader> instance by using the <xref:System.Xml.XmlReaderSettings> class and the <xref:System.Xml.XmlReader.Create%2A> method.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="4035b-695">Per altre informazioni, vedere la sezione Note della pagina di riferimento <xref:System.Xml.XmlReader>.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4035b-695">For more information, see the Remarks section of the <xref:System.Xml.XmlReader> reference page.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="4035b-696">L'utente dovrà verificare il tipo restituito.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4035b-696">The user needs to test for the returned type.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="4035b-697">Ad esempio,</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4035b-697">For example,</span></span>  
  
```csharp  
object obj = vreader.SchemaType;  
 if (obj is XmlSchemaType)  
 {  
   XmlSchemaType st = (XmlSchemaType)obj;  
   // use XmlSchemaType object  
 }  
 if (obj is XmlSchemaDatatype)  
 {  
   XmlSchemaDatatype sd = (XmlSchemaDatatype)obj;  
   Type vt = sd.ValueType;  
   // use XmlSchemaDatatype object  
       }  
```  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="4035b-698">Se viene eseguita la convalida di XML Schema, il `XmlSchemaType` o `XmlSchemaDatatype` corrisponde all'elemento corrente da leggere.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4035b-698">If XML Schema validation is being performed, the `XmlSchemaType` or `XmlSchemaDatatype` corresponds to the current element being read.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="4035b-699">Se viene eseguita la definizione di tipo documento (convalida DTD), questa proprietà restituisce `null`.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4035b-699">If document type definition (DTD validation) is being performed, this property returns `null`.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="4035b-700">`XmlSchemaDatatype` viene restituito se l'elemento corrente, o l'attributo è un tipo semplice che è possibile specificare vincoli di convalida speciale per i tipi semplici, ad esempio min e max.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4035b-700">`XmlSchemaDatatype` is returned if the current element, or attribute, is a simple type that can specify special validation constraints on the simple types, like min and max.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="4035b-701">`XmlSchemaSimpleType` viene restituito se l'elemento corrente o l'attributo è un elemento simpleType definite dall'utente.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4035b-701">`XmlSchemaSimpleType` is returned if the current element, or attribute, is a user defined simpleType.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="4035b-702">`XmlSchemaComplexType` viene restituito se l'elemento corrente è un elemento complexType definito dall'utente.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4035b-702">`XmlSchemaComplexType` is returned if the current element is a user defined complexType.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="4035b-703">Questo tipo non può essere restituito dagli attributi.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4035b-703">This type cannot be returned by attributes.</span></span>  
  
> [!NOTE]
>  <span data-ttu-id="4035b-704">Se <xref:System.Xml.XmlValidatingReader.ValidationType%2A> è stata impostata per ValidationType, alcuna informazione sul tipo di dati non viene forniti dalla DTD o schemi.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4035b-704">If <xref:System.Xml.XmlValidatingReader.ValidationType%2A> has been set to ValidationType.None, no data type information is provided from either schemas or DTDs.</span></span>  
  
> [!CAUTION]
>  <span data-ttu-id="4035b-705">Dopo aver chiamato <xref:System.Xml.XmlValidatingReader.Close%2A>, SchemaType restituiranno Null.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4035b-705">After calling <xref:System.Xml.XmlValidatingReader.Close%2A>, SchemaType will return Null.</span></span>  
  
   
  
